{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Process Name\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Digital Government Policy Coordination and ICT Infrastructure Enablement\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Service Category\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab G2G (Government to Government)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab G2C (Government to Citizen \u8211- indirect through digital platforms)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Scope\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b In Scope:} National ICT policy development; Digital government architecture and standards; Coordination of ICT projects across MDAs; Development of digital public infrastructure; Cybersecurity governance and digital trust frameworks.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Out of Scope:} Sector-specific service delivery (handled by respective MDAs).\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Triggers\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Government need for digital transformation or ICT-enabled service delivery.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 End States\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Successful:} ICT policy approved; Digital platform or infrastructure deployed; Government service digitized and operational.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Policy Context\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Constitution of Kenya (2010); Kenya Digital Economy Blueprint; Data Protection Act (2019); National ICT Policy; Kenya National Cybersecurity Strategy.\sa180\par}
